itali 's februari payment balanc in surplu itali 's over balanc of payment show a surplu of 1,461 billion lire in februari 1987 compar with a deficit of 1,145 billion in januari , provis bank of itali figur show . the februari surplu compar with a deficit of 1,578 billion lire in the same month for 1986. for the first two month of 1987 , the balanc of payment show a surplu of 302 billion lire against a deficit of 4,622 billion in the same 1986 period . the bank of itali said the cumul balanc for the first two month of 1987 doe not match the total calcul on the individu monthli figur becau of the provis natur of certain data .